to be happy.

01:24:31.484 --> 01:24:34.544
The key, my friend, is to not be picky.

01:24:34.921 --> 01:24:36.980
- Observe.
- No, wait!

01:24:38.625 --> 01:24:42.493
- Oh, no! No, no! What do we do?
- I'll go get Dad.

01:24:45.065 --> 01:24:51.334
