01:38:46.739 --> 01:38:49.606
<i>... and leaves without another word.</i>

01:38:51.877 --> 01:38:55.813
<i>The following day his review appears.</i>

01:38:58.350 --> 01:39:02.446
<i>In many ways,</i>
<i>the work of a critic is easy.</i>

01:39:02.655 --> 01:39:06.887
<i>We risk very little,</i>
<i>yet enjoy a position over those</i>

01:39:06.992 --> 01:39:11.053
