<i>of my disdain</i>

01:40:13.659 --> 01:40:18.619
<i>for Chef Gusteau's famous motto,</i>
<i>"Anyone can cook."</i>

01:40:18.931 --> 01:40:25.131
<i>But I realize only now</i>
<i>do I truly understand what he meant.</i>

01:40:25.437 --> 01:40:29.373
<i>Not everyone</i>
<i>can become a great artist,</i>

01:40:29.475 --> 01:40:33.809
<i>but a great artist</i>
