<i>than those of the genius</i>
<i>now cooking at Gusteau's,</i>

01:40:41.754 --> 01:40:44.587
<i>who is, in this critic's opinion,</i>

01:40:44.690 --> 01:40:48.922
<i>nothing less</i>
<i>than the finest chef in France.</i>

01:40:49.128 --> 01:40:51.791
